  "name": "元素反应：绽放",
  "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">生物受到</span><span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">水元素</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">与</span><span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">草元素</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">影响后，将会引发「绽放」反应，产生</span><span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">草原核</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">。</span></p>",
